# Monorepo Scaffold — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

Scaffolded a full monorepo per the [blueprint](file:///d:/Code/blueprint/blueprint_eng.md) with **Turborepo + Bun workspaces**.

## Project Structure

```
blueprint/
├── package.json              # Root: Bun workspaces, Turbo scripts
├── turbo.json                # Task pipeline (dev, build, type-check)
├── tsconfig.json             # Root strict TS config
├── .gitignore
│
├── apps/
│   ├── server/               # ElysiaJS backend (Bun)
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── index.ts              # Entry point, CORS, health check
│   │   │   ├── controllers/
│   │   │   │   └── auth.controller.ts  # Register/Login/Logout/Me + TypeBox
│   │   │   ├── services/
│   │   │   │   └── auth.service.ts     # Argon2 hashing, JWT issuance
│   │   │   └── repositories/
│   │   │       └── user.repository.ts  # Prisma queries
│   │   ├── package.json
│   │   └── tsconfig.json
│   │
│   └── web/                  # Next.js frontend (App Router)
│       ├── src/
│       │   ├── app/                    # Next.js App Router pages
│       │   ├── components/ui/          # shadcn/ui (button, input, card, label)
│       │   ├── lib/
│       │   │   ├── api.ts              # Eden Treaty client (type-safe)
│       │   │   └── utils.ts            # cn() utility
│       │   └── providers/
│       │       └── query-provider.tsx   # TanStack Query provider
│       ├── e2e/example.spec.ts         # Playwright smoke test
│       ├── playwright.config.ts
│       ├── package.json
│       └── tsconfig.json
│
└── packages/
    ├── typescript-config/    # Shared TS configs (base, nextjs, server)
    ├── db/                   # Prisma package
    │   ├── prisma/schema.prisma   # User + Account tables
    │   └── src/index.ts           # PrismaClient singleton
    └── shared/               # Shared Zod schemas, types, constants
        └── src/index.ts
```

## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| JWT plugin on **controller** not root app | Elysia child instances need their own plugin for type inference |
| `bun-types` + `jose` as **direct** deps | Bun workspace hoisting puts transitive deps in `.bun/` cache; tsc can't resolve them |
| `packages/db` extends **base.json** not server.json | DB package is shared; doesn't need Bun types |
| Password **nullable** in User model | Future-proof for OAuth providers per blueprint |
| Eden Treaty import via **relative path** | Cross-app workspace imports need relative paths for type resolution |

## Verification Results

| Check | Result |
|-------|--------|
| `bun install` | ✅ 830 packages installed |
| `turbo type-check` all packages | ✅ 4/4 successful |
| Prisma client generation | ✅ Generated successfully |
| shadcn/ui init | ✅ 4 components (button, input, card, label) |

## Next Steps

1. **Set up `DATABASE_URL`** — Copy `.env.example` to `.env` in `packages/db` and `apps/server`, fill in your Supabase credentials
2. **Run Prisma migration** — `bun run db:migrate` from root
3. **Start dev servers** — `bun run dev` from root (starts both apps via Turbo)
4. **Build your first feature** — Follow the AI workflow in the blueprint (Database → Backend → Integration → Frontend → Test)
